        Understanding Buyer Types in Brisbane's Inner East 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Knowing who is likely to buy your home, what drives their decisions, and what they are comparing yours against is one of the most underused advantages a well-prepared seller has.
      </p>
    </div>
